Its an aim-map to training the skill. There spawnpoints for 10 Ts and 10 CTs. For each T is a deagle, a glock and a ak_47 and for each CT a deagle, a usp and a m4 available.

this aim-map represents for the CT's the Stargate Center, on the way to a mission.

After all the CT's have passed the Stargate, it should close. This is untested. Should close the gate before all the Ct's have gone through, then contact me.
Thanks.
